sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant ARW as «view»<br>:AdminReportsWindow
    participant ARC as «controller»<br>:AdminReportController
    participant DB as DataModels (Event/Donation)

    note over Admin,DB: USE CASE 1: GENERATE E-CERTIFICATE
    Admin->>+ARW: request to generate e-certificates for participants
    ARW->>+ARC: generateCertificate(eventId)
    ARC->>+DB: retrieve participant & completion data
    DB-->>-ARC: return participant data
    ARC->>ARC: process & generate certificate files
    ARC-->>-ARW: return generated certificates
    ARW-->>-Admin: display success & provide download links

    note over Admin,DB: USE CASE 2: GENERATE REPORT
    Admin->>+ARW: request to view/generate report
    ARW->>+ARC: index() / process filters
    ARC->>+DB: aggregate reporting data
    DB-->>-ARC: return report data
    ARC-->>-ARW: return view with report data
    ARW-->>-Admin: display report on screen

    note over Admin,DB: EXTENDED USE CASE: PRINT REPORT
    opt EXTEND: Print / Download Report
        Admin->>+ARW: click Print or Download
        ARW->>+ARC: download() / downloadFundraisingReport()
        ARC->>ARC: format data as PDF/Excel
        ARC-->>-ARW: return file stream
        ARW-->>-Admin: prompt file download / print dialog
    end
